➜广西诗人陈熠明：一心超越了轮回的告白
http://www.sohu.com/a/429694179_100115135	30338
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201105/507228c4088c490ea37db683be358f02.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一心超越了轮回的告白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>现代诗原创作品·心灵诗幻陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你从梦里走来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我也是从梦里走来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我们曾经一起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在太阳的身边摘下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摘下思念里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片绚丽了青春的云彩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记忆里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我清楚地记得</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记得你的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">微笑在火红地灿烂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灿烂着那一场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>久违了季节的花开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我的心河里在流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流淌出那一渊牵动了想念的血脉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你花开在岁月的枝头</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但你的心却浪漫地飘落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘落在我这一片坦荡了流年的胸怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(二)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你从梦里走来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我也是从梦里走来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我们曾经一起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在月亮的身边摘下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摘下牵挂里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片璀璨了长夜的星海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>记忆里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我清楚地记得</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记得你的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">歌声在婉转地飘荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡着那一场</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>久违了历史的节拍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我的诗情里在燃烧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">燃烧起那一心清富了情感的豪迈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你站立在岁月的高台</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但你的情却疯狂地洒落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>洒落在我这一片广阔了时空的情怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦里我喝干</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一坛封存了千年的杜康</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我还是喝不出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝不出那一心滚烫了千年的豪迈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把我自己一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘摇了千年的影子一起喝下吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也许我自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>的影子里会有着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>会有着一番比酒水更为浓烈的风采</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201105/0d3ea141662044ecbdc57d133a1cfd33.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(四)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个酒杯里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历来都是坦荡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>坦荡着自己那一腔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>渐渐地涨满了高尚的胸怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我一个人喝醉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝醉了白云边</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心飘荡了过往的再来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我一个人喝醉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝醉了天涯里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一情苍茫了流年的花开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦里我喝干</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一坛埋藏了千年的杜康</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我还是喝不出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝不出那一情豪放了千年的气慨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把我自己一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘荡了千年的脚步一起喝下吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也许我自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>的脚步里会有着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>会有着一番比酒度更为浓烈的豪迈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(六)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个酒杯里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历来都是流淌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流淌着自己那一心</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>渐渐地澎湃了热恋的浪海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时光里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我一个人喝醉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝醉了黎明里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一片飘荡了渴望的云彩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">时光里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我一个人喝醉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝醉了黄昏里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一情梦幻了别去的远爱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201105/35e76536a93f44868e1cb8640f5b6b0a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(七)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我没有神的豪迈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也没有神的豪迈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>所以我们</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都没有办法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有办法摘下天边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片飘荡了时光的云彩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>触摸不到你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>触摸不到你那一张</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>漂亮地灿烂了云霞的脸庞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是因为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有思念挡住</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>挡住眼泪里那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>苍茫地模煳了岁月的神态</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我用脚步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我用心跳的脚步去踏上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>踏上那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>被流年封存了高尚的瑶台</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回头时我看见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看见三生石上璀璨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>璀璨着你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心明亮了天涯的真爱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(八)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我没有仙的气慨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也没有仙的气慨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>所以我们</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都没有办法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有办法走出梦里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片涌动了生命的云海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感应不到你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感应不到你那一律</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>热情地跳动了岁月的心跳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是因为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有牵挂挡住</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>挡住枝头上那一片</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>浪漫地怒放了季节的花开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我用平仄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我用心跳的平仄去写下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写下那一诗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>被轮回放慢了速度的歌海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回头时我看见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看见相思树下灿烂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灿烂着你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一眼亮丽了云霞的光彩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(九)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不要太过偏信</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不要太过地去偏信自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一颗麻醉了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>时光的痴心会飞落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞落于春天里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片火红了世界的花海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泪水淹没过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我眼里泛滥的泪水淹没过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淹没过风月桥上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片渲染了黎明的云彩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201105/996a9819fffe487a8ca0930ae4fa924d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我一个人真的不应该</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不应该在太阳初起的黎明唤醒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唤醒了你那一片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沉睡了千年的梦海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如果你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一颗心真的不想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真的不想从</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥遥离去的远航里归来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无论如何都翻不开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻不开你梦里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片冷漠了岁月的情怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(<strong>十一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不要太过相信自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不要太过地去相信自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一首芬芳了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">枝头的情诗会飘落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘落于春风里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一情浪漫了宇宙的情怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念滚烫过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我心里疯狂的热血滚烫过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滚烫过碧水云间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一片流淌了黄昏的感慨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十二)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我一个人真的不应该</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不应该在月亮初起的夜晚摘下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>摘下了你那一片</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悬挂了千年的星海</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗心真的不想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>真的不想从</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥遥离去的流浪里归来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么我</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论如何都等不到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等不到你梦里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一片苍凉了流年的情怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201105/427deb222dc241ef9d2f5bbd93a4f117.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用三分的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想念去感应吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我自己</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>却怎么也感应不到</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感应不到过往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你那每一律心跳的节拍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>目光里潮湿地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>潮湿地滑落下了崭新的灵感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可那一些灵感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的情种里就是诠释不出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诠释不出我对你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对你那一心超越了历史的表白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十四)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落寞着一情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘落了谎花的感慨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的枝头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不再拥有着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拥有着你那一春</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灿烂了花开的情怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>两行热泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘落于风中的两行热泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一行热泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是随着别离</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的夕阳默默地去梦里追寻着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>追寻着那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥远了轮回的过去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热泪是随着飘落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的心思惆怅地在梦外羡慕着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>羡慕着那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>漫长了岁月的将来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用七分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的牵挂去感应吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我自己却</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怎么也感应不到</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感应不到过往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你那每一心灼热的存在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>岁月里遗憾地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遗憾地丢失下了痴情的花开</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可那一些遗憾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的怒放里就是芬芳不出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>芬芳不出我对你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对你那一心超越了轮回的告白</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201105/22157604a0eb42c599a569f50714f2f5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十六)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍凉着一夜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘落了飞花的无奈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的枝头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不再浪漫着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浪漫着你那一春</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喜悦了花开的重来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>两行热泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘落于雨中的两行热泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一行热泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是随着别离</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的烟雨悄悄地去梦里追赶着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>追赶着那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>漫长了轮回的期待</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另一行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">热泪是随着断裂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的心情疼痛地在梦外贪婪着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贪婪着那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>漫长了时光的未来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(十七)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">退隐在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">石头缝里的青苔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个今天又一个今天地编织着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>编织着那</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一片又一片爬满了思念的情怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也许是我的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">概念成立不了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>成立不了梦想里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个花开了前缘的真爱</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以你还在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一年四季地瞎猜着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>瞎猜着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沉没在我心海里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一船飘摇了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘摇了风雨和飘摇了阳光的风采</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十八)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>苦涩了岁月的眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在那一心距离了归来的日子里感慨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">断断续续地感慨着清风里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那每一粒无影地负重了热恋的尘埃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长夜总是</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在流萤的纷扰里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>把我的心思若隐若现地去点燃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去点燃起黑暗中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一方淹没了情感的豪迈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201105/aeffa8fdc38c4d7eb3fbcc74924edda1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201105/99577ed0e5504d4cb8c966246eedf677.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201105/cd207513ef304581937d414e9d525984.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
